Best practices

* Log files

When running with logging to stdout/stderr Docker stores the log in a json file, and it is recommended to specify a max size for the log file to rotate, and a max number of files to keep. E.g. --log-opt max-size=50m --log-opt max-file=10

    --log-opt max-size=50m --log-opt max-file=10

https://docs.docker.com/engine/admin/logging/overview/

